summary: Next chapter. Childhood fairytales have chapters, which emulate childlike whims. She wrote of chalk on the sidewalk, and holding...
body:
Next chapter. Childhood fairytales have chapters, which emulate childlike whims. She wrote of chalk on the sidewalk, and holding on to blazing self respect. She hints of her poems, and letting go.

I think ts7 could be about growing up… about respecting yourself… and letting go of your past… your reputation… and just… moving on.
